<br>
She had this...icky feeling around Ares.  And he wouldn't go away.  She felt as though at any moment something bad were going to happen.  Anytime he was around she felt tense.  Without knowing how, or why, she felt as if he were constantly degrading her while building her up at the same time.<br>
<br>
She wandered until she stood in the middle of the village nearing tears.  She didn't want to bother her Queen with a little girl's problem.  Who would she go to?<br>
<br>
She stood there, looking from hut to hut, wondering who she could talk to that could help.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#993300>(3/19/01 3:48:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> a little help</span><hr size=1> :::Suddenly, a voice spoke to Nicodema from behind.  Hera had appeared quietly, no cry of peacocks or flash of lightening.  Even the winter was getting to the Queen of the Gods:::<br>
<br>
Does my son trouble you, dear Amazon? :::She wore a black cloak decorated in peacock feathers.  Her head was covered by the cloak's black fur that warmed her cheeks.   Bits of wavy auburn tendrils flowed from underneath the hood.  Upon her face was warm smile.::: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nicodemaalcinoe>Nicodema Alcinoe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 32<br> <font color=#993300>(3/22/01 2:57:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/xnicodemax/images/nicodmea.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: a little help</span><hr size=1> ::She whipped around, caught off guard.  She shivered inside the fur cloak, not only from the cold, but from being spoken directly to by the awesome Goddess.::<br>
<br>
Y-yes ma'am.  I'm afraid I don't understand what he wants of me.  He says he wants to help me:  to make me into a better warrior.  But each time he's around I get the feeling that he's there to make fun of me and treat me like a child.<br>
<br>
::She bites her lip::  Please, may I trouble you for some advice, your highness? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 29<br> <font color=#993300>(3/28/01 6:23:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> troubled amazon</span><hr size=1> Hera quietly listened as Nicodema spoke to her of her son, Ares.  She had known that her son of war had been trying to court this amazon.  Much like he had any warrior women he thought he might could possibly make his queen of war...or could just use.<br>
&quot;First, let us to a warmer place,&quot; Hera smiled. &quot;For I care not for this frozen air.  Shall we?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Melousa</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(3/31/01 10:36:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ~stops, hearing Hera and the othre amazon ~</span><hr size=1> ~ Feeling quite alone, Melousa walks through the snow, her extended belly a bit bigger, she wraps her furs around her tightly, enjoying the cold air, her heart empty, she feels more alone now then ever before, hearing Hera's voice she stops, not wanting to evesdrop, but she doesnt know what else to do, she hears the other Amazon talk of Ares and how he is trying to court her, she looks down to her belly, tears welling in her eyes, knowing that she was stupid to trust a him of all gods, a bit pissed she hasnt heard or seen him since he planted his seed in her, she sighs and turns walking away slowly in the other direction~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nicodemaalcinoe>Nicodema Alcinoe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#993300>(4/4/01 3:10:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ::agrees::</span><hr size=1> ::Nods:: Of course, as you wish.  Do you have somewhere in mind? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#993300>(5/19/01 9:19:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: </span><hr size=1> ::Looking down from Olympus Poseidon looks at Hera and the amazon. Poseidon appears by Hera's side invisible to the amazon. He looks to the amazon and then to Hera. Being heard only by Hera Poseidon speaks.::<br>
<br>
&quot;My sister, leave these mortals alone. If your son wants to court this woman let him. What right has she to blame a god for her troubles or sorrows?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 67<br> <font color=#993300>(6/4/01 3:17:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A tavern</span><hr size=1> Hera leads the amazon into a warm tavern.  She appears disquised to the other mortals as they walk in.  Then frowns upon hearing her brother.  She sends him a message.  ~*Stay out of this.  If she wishes not to be w/ my son.  Then her wish should be respected.*~<br>
They walk to a table near the fire and sit down. Hera turns her eyes to Nico and smiles gently. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 57<br> <font color=#993300>(6/5/01 4:22:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re::</span><hr size=1> ::The great God Poseidon heeds his sisters words and respctfully backs away and fades.:: <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A> at: 6/14/01 9:51:21 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessage?topicID=226.topic"> << Prev Topic </a> &nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessage?topicID=214.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.emailToFriend?topicID=178.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.threadControl?topicID=178.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Modera